title: Below Deck Med: Putting the B in Honey
description:
Below Deck Med finally gets rid of the b Honey and the kosher crew, but no one can forget the sting.
This week's bonus is a shot by shot breakdown of the Real Housewives of Orange County Season 13 trailer. To hear it, become a Patreon member at Patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens.
***Limited Edition Give Them BenRon tees at crappensmerch.com avail through May!
**Crappens Live is coming to San Francisco, Phoenix, Irvine, DC, and has added second shows in Atlanta and Philadelphia! Find ticket links at watchwhatcrappens.com
